    "body": [
        {
            "format": "basic_html",
            "processed": "<p><a href=\"https://www.ultralytics.com/\">Ultralytics</a><span> creates cutting-edge, state-of-the-art (SOTA) </span><a href=\"https://www.ultralytics.com/yolo\">YOLO models</a><span> built on years of foundational research in computer vision and AI. Constantly updated for performance and flexibility, our models are </span><strong>fast</strong><span>, </span><strong>accurate</strong><span>, and </span><strong>easy to use</strong><span>. They excel at </span><a href=\"https://docs.ultralytics.com/tasks/detect/\">object detection</a><span>, </span><a href=\"https://docs.ultralytics.com/modes/track/\">tracking</a><span>, </span><a href=\"https://docs.ultralytics.com/tasks/segment/\">instance segmentation</a><span>, </span><a href=\"https://docs.ultralytics.com/tasks/classify/\">image classification</a><span>, and </span><a href=\"https://docs.ultralytics.com/tasks/pose/\">pose estimation</a><span> tasks.</span></p>",
